name: RED & WHITE stripe Vintage Two Piece Swimsuit Bikini
description:
RED & WHITE stripe Vintage Two Piece Swimsuit Bikini

size: 7/8 womens

measurements: 

each triangle for top is 8.5" across bottom, 6.5" from top tip to bottom center, 22" side tie straps (each), 27" neck straps (each) (mannequin is a 34 b)

- bottoms measure 28" hips before stretch (mannequin is 33" hips and the bottoms are a perfect fit), 8.5" down front to crotch.

materials: feels like cotton and spandex or lycra for stretch. 

colors: red and white

condition: good pre-owned vintage, no stains, not over stretched. the tops white ties are replacement ties from the original ones.
